(1530, 1, 'Mukta', 'The style conscious, career oriented youth who seeks advice on every thing from beauty, fitness style to education &amp; careers.', '', '', ''),
(1531, 1, 'Saras Salil - Gujarati', 'Saras Salil is a popular Indian magazine. It contains unique mix of commentaries on social and political issues, and varied articles on society, sex, fiction and entertainment. Saras Salil is published in 5 languages and has a highest readership according to IRS 2009 R1 in India . Incidentally, Saras Salil is placed second in the all magazines chart.', '', '', ''),
